text: FIFA Soccer 95 is a 1994 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts FIFA series published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the Sega Genesis in November 1994. It is a sequel to FIFA International Soccer and the second game in the FIFA series. It is the only FIFA title to not be released on PC.
